{"tid":244383,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【電騙又來了】義氣男誤信「前同事」捲內地刑事案 中招失9萬人仔","createTime":"2017-05-15T11:43:08.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-15T12:22:27.000Z","uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"b44ffffcc79f6bb0b83b828693a6736612f2ec4e","tid":244383,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-15T11:43:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/e-paper/20170515/large/1494847965_d4d8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170515%2Flarge%2F1494847965_d4d8.jpg&h=ae1fba04&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n又有電話騙案！早上9時許，警方接獲一名34歲男子報案稱今早收到一名陌生男子來電，對方自稱是他的前同事，訛稱在內地涉及一些刑事案件，要求男事主匯款應急。男事主不虞有詐，按騙徒指示匯款9萬元人民幣至一個內地銀行戶口，其後他致電該名前同事發現沒有此事，始懷疑受騙。警方經初步調查後，案件列作以欺騙手段取得財產，交由元朗警區刑事調查隊第四隊跟進，暫未有人被捕。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/breaking/20170515/56697546\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fbreaking%2F20170515%2F56697546&d=RGPktlJYpqjIeXpZRAkgw54f2li5K%2Fs6EGgmwhpeblA%3D&h=af6d6387\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fbreaking%2F20170515%2F56697546&h=a61d9fdd\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/breaking/20170515/56697546</a>"},{"pid":"5513e9f189928941eeecd3b2843033fb2b19fa86","tid":244383,"uid":52651,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-15T11:51:14.000Z","msg":"呢d案似乎破唔到，重要日日有人中&hellip;&hellip;"},{"pid":"64cfe6a13ffd2be6eccc269f75328f4dd166a433","tid":244383,"uid":102056,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-15T12:09:55.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"272d9faa6a821cbaba0d755ba9d2e7a09910d0df","tid":244383,"uid":20227,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-15T12:22:27.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"}]}